"title": "2072: Jesus Christ, righteousness of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "2072",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Jesus Christ pleased his Father perfectly in his life on earth and in his death. He now gives believers a new status before God and a new power for living.</p>\n<h2>The promised Messiah will be righteous</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Zech9:9\">ZEC 9:9</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps45:7\">PSA 45:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa53:11\">ISA 53:11</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:5-Jer23:6\">JER 23:5–23:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:15\">JER 33:15</a></p>\n<h3>The promised Messiah will establish righteousness</h3>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps72:1-Ps72:4\">PSA 72:1–72:4</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa9:7\">ISA 9:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa11:3-Isa11:5\">ISA 11:3–11:5</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ's own righteousness</h2>\n<h3>Righteousness is characteristic of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts22:14\">ACT 22:14</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:14\">ACT 3:14</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts7:52\">ACT 7:52</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Tim4:8\">2TI 4:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:8-Heb1:9\">HEB 1:8–1:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:1\">1JN 2:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John2:29\">1JN 2:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John3:7\">1JN 3:7</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's obedience shows his righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:28-John8:29\">JHN 8:28–8:29</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John4:34\">JHN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:38\">JHN 6:38</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John12:49-John12:50\">JHN 12:49–12:50</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:31\">JHN 14:31</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:8\">PHP 2:8</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb5:8-Heb5:9\">HEB 5:8–5:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:9\">HEB 10:9</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ judges righteously</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:30\">JHN 5:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ is declared not guilty</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:14-Luke23:15\">LUK 23:14–23:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:4\">LUK 23:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John19:6\">JHN 19:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts3:13\">ACT 3:13</a></p>\n<h3>Jesus Christ's righteousness recognised by others</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:47\">LUK 23:47</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mark10:17-Mark10:18\">MRK 10:17–10:18</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:18-Luke18:19\">LUK 18:18–18:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke23:41\">LUK 23:41</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts10:38\">ACT 10:38</a></p>\n<h2>Consequences of Jesus Christ's righteousness</h2>\n<h3>God justifies believers on account of the righteousness of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom5:18-Rom5:19\">ROM 5:18–5:19</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23-Rom3:26\">ROM 3:23–3:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet3:18\">1PE 3:18</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet1:1\">2PE 1:1</a></p>\n<h3>All who believe share in the righteousness of Jesus Christ</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor1:30\">1CO 1:30</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:21-Rom3:22\">ROM 3:21–3:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:6\">ROM 4:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom4:24\">ROM 4:24</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:30\">ROM 9:30</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom10:3-Rom10:4\">ROM 10:3–10:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor5:21\">2CO 5:21</a></p>\n<h3>Believers live by and for Jesus Christ's righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil1:11\">PHP 1:11</a></strong> <em>One of Paul's prayers for Christians.</em> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom6:18\">ROM 6:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:10\">ROM 8:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet2:24\">1PE 2:24</a></p>",
